The paper proposes a framework for solving the task of Visual Dialog, which involves reasoning and understanding of visual and language modalities. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. However, since the paper focuses on multi-modal deep learning techniques that combine visual and language representations, it is most likely to belong to the cs.CV sub-category. The other sub-categories are also possible because they are related to the task of Visual Dialog, but they are less likely because they are broader and may not capture the specific focus of the paper.
